6ea447","tid":277383,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"點傷先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe96f6e3bf3b479d4708b2d8021ca9edb12d600f","tid":277383,"uid":52875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有一忽仔one day con列咗係眼入邊成一個月仲未出返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前我個fd都係咁<br />\n長期眼紅<br />\n最後去睇專科<br />\n個醫生話d碎片割到隻眼出血<br />\n所以長期眼紅<br />\n之後個醫生幫佢夾返d碎片出黎"},{"pid":"89a779f4c239542a3106461901439748aa503a23","tid":277383,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點傷先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉屌其實我都唔知<br />\n但係咁漂眼水<br />\n係唔係要買洗眼水?"},{"pid":"f646c06c39f7ca0db41854f19c2da146925f1411","tid":277383,"uid":53923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Chlor Oph可利安眼藥水<br />\n見佢寫可用於眼部創傷<br />\n應該藥房有掛<br />\n用左冇改善記住睇醫生呀</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無邊隻眼藥水英國有賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔清楚英國有咩眼藥水喎<br />\n你隻眼咩情況先？<br />\n單純紅筋/發炎/feel到有野係眼入面/出血/有割傷？<br />\n前面三樣普通消炎眼藥水應該得架啦<br />\n後面兩樣你都係快啲睇醫生"},{"pid":"0f67597945098f9b3e48b997a2408643011dadd4","tid":277383,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Chlor Oph可利安眼藥水<br />\n見佢寫可用於眼部創傷<br />\n應該藥房有掛<br />\n用左冇改善記住睇醫生呀</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無邊隻眼藥水英國有賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔清楚英國有咩眼藥水喎<br />\n你隻眼咩情況先？<br />\n單純紅筋/發炎/feel到有野係眼入面/出血/有割傷？<br />\n前面三樣普通消炎眼藥水應該得架啦<br />\n後面兩樣你都係快啲睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n發炎 係咁漂眼水<br />\n但我唔識買眼藥水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗眼水又得唔得?"},{"pid":"62877fe28a3e65ef6758ab5cf083ba3591e93de6","tid":277383,"uid":90005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Chlor Oph可利安眼藥水<br />\n見佢寫可用於眼部創傷<br />\n應該藥房有掛<br />\n用左冇改善記住睇醫生呀</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無邊隻眼藥水英國有賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔清楚英國有咩眼藥水喎<br />\n你隻眼咩情況先？<br />\n單純紅筋/發炎/feel到有野係眼入面/出血/有割傷？<br />\n前面三樣普通消炎眼藥水應該得架啦<br />\n後面兩樣你都係快啲睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n發炎 係咁漂眼水<br />\n但我唔識買眼藥水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗眼水又得唔得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發炎係痕定痛？<br />\n如果痕可先試眼藥水<br />\n唔得一定要睇醫生<br />\n如果痛即時去睇醫生唔好諗<br />\n眼得一對有咩事好大獲<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過眼紅以為普通發炎<br />\n醫生話係細菌感染搞左成兩個月先好返<br />\n頭兩三星期係要隔日去覆診咁濟"},{"pid":"24fd765bc70fb5aee901ce9ec047e35fe598903d","tid":277383,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Chlor Oph可利安眼藥水<br />\n見佢寫可用於眼部創傷<br />\n應該藥房有掛<br />\n用左冇改善記住睇醫生呀</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無邊隻眼藥水英國有賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔清楚英國有咩眼藥水喎<br />\n你隻眼咩情況先？<br />\n單純紅筋/發炎/feel到有野係眼入面/出血/有割傷？<br />\n前面三樣普通消炎眼藥水應該得架啦<br />\n後面兩樣你都係快啲睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n發炎 係咁漂眼水<br />\n但我唔識買眼藥水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗眼水又得唔得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發炎係痕定痛？<br />\n如果痕可先試眼藥水<br />\n唔得一定要睇醫生<br />\n如果痛即時去睇醫生唔好諗<br />\n眼得一對有咩事好大獲<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過眼紅以為普通發炎<br />\n醫生話係細菌感染搞左成兩個月先好返<br />\n頭兩三星期係要隔日去覆診咁濟</blockquote><br />\n無感覺 得眼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f1015d49f605072ffb869ea7b1216bc89207ff","tid":277383,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T21:18:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有一忽仔one day con列咗係眼入邊成一個月仲未出返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前我個fd都係咁<br />\n長期眼紅<br />\n最後去睇專科<br />\n個醫生話d碎片割到隻眼出血<br />\n所以長期眼紅<br />\n之後個醫生幫佢夾返d碎片出黎</blockquote><br />\n屌好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a61739373ebad3e4eb7d925778891c8031b6671","tid":277383,"uid":122054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T22:11:12.000Z","msg":"淚然唔知岩唔岩?<br />\n普通野 人造淚水"},{"pid":"0eb791ca11c1d3af5317d8047330a973fb6d71f0","tid":277383,"uid":74191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:22:36.000Z","msg":"隻眼有無出眼膠"},{"pid":"0d530ebca907d3f6450a971756da5222e652e42e","tid":277383,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T00:04:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻眼有無出眼膠</blockquote><br />\n有"},{"pid":"76ec9043b3b964772c7e2ba2170c3e57b72